            {
                "title": "When we want to add the meaning of 'only' to a noun, we use the particle '만'.",
                "details": "We append 만 to the end of a noun, and this also adds the meaning of the noun being the topic/subject of the sentence as well. So when we use 만, we don't use 는/은 or 이/가 with it."
